{"tid":962262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊（700）：港版微信錢包將接入內地86萬家商店","createTime":"2018-12-30T17:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T15:39:57.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"416cb25f1f31e64fca37717142542a3ed462f1bb","tid":962262,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"騰訊宣佈，由即日起港版微信支付可接入內地實體商戶。<br />\n<br />\n港版微信支付可接入 86 萬家內地商戶，包括大型百貨超市和餐廳，並可以用港版微信錢包，使用深圳地鐵和滴滴出行等交通服務，每次支付都會以人民幣價格、換成港元金額結算，騰訊暫時不收手續費。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊表示，今次實現雙向跨境服務，能夠促進兩地市場流通，推動粵港澳大灣區共建金融科技新生態，明年還會連接更多內地商戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/372778776633288/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F372778776633288%2F&d=g%2F9XyKfhmpymZxUQnmC8ATA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5b3fd941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/372778776633288/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大利好"},{"pid":"6ddd778919fbcf20f50a651bcf6229f041e3f6e5","tid":962262,"uid":13008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"416cb25f1f31e64fca37717142542a3ed462f1bb","tid":962262,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"騰訊宣佈，由即日起港版微信支付可接入內地實體商戶。<br />\n<br />\n港版微信支付可接入 86 萬家內地商戶，包括大型百貨超市和餐廳，並可以用港版微信錢包，使用深圳地鐵和滴滴出行等交通服務，每次支付都會以人民幣價格、換成港元金額結算，騰訊暫時不收手續費。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊表示，今次實現雙向跨境服務，能夠促進兩地市場流通，推動粵港澳大灣區共建金融科技新生態，明年還會連接更多內地商戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/372778776633288/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F372778776633288%2F&d=g%2F9XyKfhmpymZxUQnmC8ATA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5b3fd941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/372778776633288/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif